Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像平常一樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“哇，好軟喔\N好像埃爾斯的胸部一樣”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼食慾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是一件大事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到愛莉卡竟然食慾不振
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要下雪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是茜姊姊跟卡迪亞國\N克勞捷克家的和也先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是看錯了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去，這個借妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:00:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是珍珠第一名的茜姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會犯錯才對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯錯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逼我解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉\N給我慢著！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人最近\N越來越像好拍檔了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心悸動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿盈內心 開始散放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會如此不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日一定會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算中途受挫也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能踏出小小的一步 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嶄新的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第13話 在茜色的天空…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然對想成為Meister的妳做出…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜·索瓦娑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到學園長室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，要我成為Meister？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然事出突然\N想必驚嚇到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服侍查理國王的Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅莎麗·克勞迪爾因為要結婚\N所以要從乙HiME的身份引退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅莎麗姊姊要結婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而妳則優先被選為\N佛羅倫斯王家代代相傳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“清戀的孔雀石”的繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是學生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並不是沒有先例
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是認為妳的實力沒有問題\N所以開出特例
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也已經派人通知索瓦娑家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊相當欣喜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳，女士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister茜·索瓦娑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學中就被任命為Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是本校也是首開先例吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛羅倫斯的宮殿很華麗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯妳們\N負責姊姊的房間對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有多聽說些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這件事情之後還沒碰面過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和也的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加迪亞和佛羅倫斯\N從以前以來關係就不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用懂也沒有關係的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早先一步實現夢想了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝福妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，千繪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我總覺得\N還沒什麼實際感受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想炫耀就乾脆點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，畢竟發生了類似\N干擾健行考試等許多狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜不在是一大損失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有妳在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會充分引導學妹的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得胸口一直悶悶的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是醒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳記不記得自己突然昏倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜突然把妳扛了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說妳從之前就怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是奈米機械失控就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？有哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，陽子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然是生病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈米機械是沒有異常啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這確實是一種病徵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說的好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是連神佛都醫不了的病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依狀況不同妳可能會承受\N比死還痛苦的經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆…婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有沒有聽過\N“炎綬的紅玉”的故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME列傳第109篇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徬徨在神離之森裡的\N悲情乙HiME魂魄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“炎綬的紅玉”傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這故事已經久遠到\N可以成為傳說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，只是幾年前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候，這裡出了一個\N非常優秀的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的未來發展性備受矚目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業的時候決定繼承\N那個“炎綬的紅玉”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她在那時候\N與某位男性相戀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從入學時就已經決定\N將來要服侍某位主人的她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很煩惱自己究竟該成為乙HiME\N實現夢想還是選擇愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真祖卻判斷她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該要成為五柱之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？五柱不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像學園長和靜留姊這樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有特定的主人，服侍真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,責任就是守護乙HiME存在本身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常榮譽的職位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對“炎綬的紅玉”來說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最痛苦的宣判
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在煩惱之際\N為了能自己決定將來的路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往能夠看透未來的\N神之住所——神離之森去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後她就再也沒有從那裡回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說她的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍然徘徊在\N那座陰暗的森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人真是笨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫她要愛上男性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與男性戀愛和成為乙HiME\N本來就不能並行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在加爾德羅貝\N才會注重與姊姊之間的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之中\N能夠培養愛戀之情就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情報指出在阿爾泰國境附近\N目擊到那個男人…史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留，妳可以跑一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果夏樹希望我去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我現在最希望妳留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎綬的紅玉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是陽子老師怎麼突然\N提起這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道遲早會碰到這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是妳不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要被拉到第三名了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多事情很麻煩的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直被叮矚要成為一個Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有這個意願
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，太沒魄力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照自己想做的去做就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算捨棄一切也無妨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我辦不到，阿和也辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷，這不是妳的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三和弦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～真是的，麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡有喜歡上任何人過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛真是奇妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在相遇之前完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至應該連有這個人存在\N都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻會因為那個人\N無心的一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到歡喜或難過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想著那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:11:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口就會縮緊起來，很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…墜入情網呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌和編織者與守護者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那似乎是\N啓動古風琴的必要條件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來讓你找尋\N真正公主的下落是有價值了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托記錄在那裡面的資料之福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落的高次物質化技術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能夠做出\N更接近那個原型的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,場面話就省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然啊，大公殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你馬上就能理解這個的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，突然找你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會，我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳因為工作\N要暫時離開學園一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間過得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過不久妳就會升上珍珠了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟過去的我很像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳別多繞無謂的遠路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好看清前方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到中途為止我們一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…阿和…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡小茜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜妳不也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡啊，我最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…\N沒辦法捨棄國家…還有夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和你不也一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說有朝一日\N要為國家出力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此而努力唸書的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳送我到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工的時間趕得上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…靜留姊有談過戀愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜…靜留姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，好好加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，小茜妳等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:13:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜學姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴獸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們快點去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我也參戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳瞭解這代表什麼意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我是乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找出奴獸的操縱者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的人就交給妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人這麼多的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能沒當上乙HiME…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能沒當上Meister啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是希望如此才努力到現在的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟過去的不太一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我調查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被石頭吞噬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了…阿和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼不阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡茜學姊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…也是有無計可施的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要由自己來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是，覺得有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太會講
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肅靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在進行Meister冊封儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“清戀的孔雀石”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister茜·索瓦娑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意發誓認同這位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理·夏爾·洛·杜·佛羅倫斯八世為主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為守護他而與之共有生命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以乙HiME的身份\N奉獻自己一切的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:19:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就將授予妳的那契約貴石\N獻給主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我會永遠疼愛妳的，茜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我所期望的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且慢！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是喜歡妳，我愛妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了妳我可以拋家棄國
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都可以捨棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法成為你的乙HiME…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔～真有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊，攔住那兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種不吉利的事情\N怎麼可以允許
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜姊姊…太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害耶，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捨棄夢想，為愛而生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是一種生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳會不會有點羨慕呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會成為Meister-乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊，妮依娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳呢？螞蟻仔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越在意那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個人無心的一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到歡喜或難過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正對妳來說還太早吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜啦，成長中的螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想著那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口就會縮緊起來，很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要…墜入情網呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙…騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快告訴我這不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留傳回來重力子通訊信號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在羅繆勒斯跟萊姆斯國境處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生乙HiME之間的戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.66,0:22:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.44,0:22:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.61,0:22:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:22:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.09,0:23:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.88,0:23:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.20,0:23:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（少女的S·0·S)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是戀愛的話\N真的就無法成為乙HiME嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說，戀愛之後\N做了某些事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.87,0:23:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某些事是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.80,0:23:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯，交給妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們實際演習一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.64,0:23:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依琳娜～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…埃爾斯妳等…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
